• Do not use the plugin with people you don't fully trust.
• You may end up getting hacked with malicious scripts in the projects. 
• Backup your projects before any use or you may end up breaking them.
• The plugin is NOT complete and is still under development.
• You will encounter bugs and half-working features.
[/indent]

